## ğŸ Local Run Instructions

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- Node.js 18+
- npm or yarn

### 1. Install Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### 2. Install Backend
```bash
cd backend
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

### 3. (Optional) Run with Docker
```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

